different.

00:02:54.500 --> 00:02:56.530
And I know YouTube is--

00:02:56.530 --> 00:02:59.320
they're not shy about writing
about what they see.

00:02:59.320 --> 00:03:00.230
Should we talk about that?

00:03:00.230 --> 00:03:01.100
What's going on there?

00:03:01.100 --> 00:03:02.840
ALAN STEWART: Let's do that.

00:03:02.840 --> 00:03:06.350
In my right eye, I have a
condition called band

00:03:06.350 --> 00:03:09.180
keratopathy, which is a
buildup of mineral.

00:03:09.180 --> 00:03:10.416
So it's just cloudy.

00:03:10.416 --> 00:03:14.090
And I can't see out of
that eye at all.

00:03:14.090 --> 00:03:18.250
My left eye is going
the same way.

00:03:18.250 --> 00:03:21.770
So my vision in my left eye
is not perfect either.

00:03:21.770 --> 00:03:22.690
BRADY HARAN: OK.

00:03:22.690 --> 00:03:23.680
There you go.

00:03:23.680 --> 00:03:24.760
