ALAN STEWART: Oh.

00:04:59.920 --> 00:05:00.440
Do you know?

00:05:00.440 --> 00:05:03.360
BRADY HARAN: No.

00:05:03.360 --> 00:05:05.965
You're all very quickly going
to learn that I have no idea

00:05:05.965 --> 00:05:07.990
what any notes are.

00:05:07.990 --> 00:05:09.710
Do you know?

00:05:09.710 --> 00:05:11.690
ALAN STEWART: Sometimes I
have to think about it.

00:05:11.690 --> 00:05:13.050
BRADY HARAN: I'll play
a different one.

00:05:13.050 --> 00:05:13.290
It won't be the same one.

00:05:13.290 --> 00:05:14.330
ALAN STEWART: Was it G?

00:05:14.330 --> 00:05:14.675
BRADY HARAN: I don't know.

00:05:14.675 --> 00:05:14.845
It was one of these ones.

00:05:14.845 --> 00:05:15.704
ALAN STEWART: Go on, go
on, play it again.

00:05:15.704 --> 00:05:16.970
BRADY HARAN: It was
one of these ones.

00:05:16.970 --> 00:05:17.950
ALAN STEWART: One
of these ones.

00:05:17.950 --> 00:05:19.150
BRADY HARAN: I don't even
know what one it was.

00:05:19.150 --> 00:05:20.230
ALAN STEWART: And I
can play it again.

00:05:20.230 --> 00:05:20.500
[NOTE PLAYING]

00:05:20.500 --> 00:05:21.780
ALAN STEWART: It was B.

00:05:21.780 --> 00:05:23.170
BRADY HARAN: It was B.

00:05:23.170 --> 00:05:25.080
ALAN STEWART: I was way off.

00:05:25.080 --> 00:05:26.490
But I was able to
play it again.

00:05:26.490 --> 00:05:28.050
BRADY HARAN: You were.

00:05:28.050 --> 00:05:29.565
So what's that, semi-perfect
pitch, maybe?

00:05:29.565 --> 00:05:30.920
ALAN STEWART: I think, yeah.

00:05:30.920 --> 00:05:32.050
Perfect is a stretch.

00:05:32.050 --> 00:05:36.746
Let's just say able to hear a
note and play it back again.

00:05:36.746 --> 00:05:39.550
BRADY HARAN: Now you're not
a professional musician.

00:05:39.550 --> 00:05:40.740
That's not how you
make your living.

00:05:40.740 --> 00:05:41.270
ALAN STEWART: No.

00:05:41.270 --> 00:05:42.120
BRADY HARAN: What's your job?

00:05:42.120 --> 00:05:43.950
ALAN STEWART: I am a teacher.

00:05:43.950 --> 00:05:48.440
I teach A-level physics at
Queen Mary's College.

00:05:48.440 --> 00:05:50.728
I've been a teacher
for four years.

00:05:50.728 --> 00:05:52.360
And I love it.

00:05:52.360 --> 00:05:54.310
