00:21:22.555 --> 00:21:24.480
I particularly like this one.

00:21:24.480 --> 00:21:25.350
[NOTES PLAYING]

00:21:25.350 --> 00:21:28.510
ALAN STEWART: This is the
orchestral percussion kit on

00:21:28.510 --> 00:21:29.470
the keyboard.

00:21:29.470 --> 00:21:36.210
And it's got some nice, low
