00:22:04.540 --> 00:22:05.320
[NOTE PLAYING]

00:22:05.320 --> 00:22:06.485
ALAN STEWART: And then 2.

00:22:06.485 --> 00:22:07.720
[NOTES PLAYING]

00:22:07.720 --> 00:22:09.522
ALAN STEWART: And then 3.

00:22:09.522 --> 00:22:10.366
[NOTES PLAYING]

00:22:10.366 --> 00:22:11.175
ALAN STEWART: And then 5.

00:22:11.175 --> 00:22:13.296
[NOTES PLAYING]

00:22:13.296 --> 00:22:17.400
ALAN STEWART: And those can be
