I think what it was was I think
you said you were going

00:28:28.430 --> 00:28:29.765
to do a video--

00:28:29.765 --> 00:28:30.200
yes.

00:28:30.200 --> 00:28:31.640
You said you were going to do
a video where you were going

00:28:31.640 --> 00:28:34.050
to measure pi using pies.

00:28:34.050 --> 00:28:36.730
And could I come up
with some music?

00:28:36.730 --> 00:28:38.910
It could be based
on pi, you said.

