00:30:05.240 --> 00:30:07.032
BRADY HARAN: I believe so.

00:30:07.032 --> 00:30:08.930
ALAN STEWART: So yeah.

00:30:08.930 --> 00:30:10.490
BRADY HARAN: We ended up with
