[NOTE PLAYING]

00:34:07.960 --> 00:34:08.490
ALAN STEWART: The fifth note.

00:34:08.490 --> 00:34:08.620
[NOTE PLAYING]

00:34:08.620 --> 00:34:09.642
ALAN STEWART: The ninth.

00:34:09.642 --> 00:34:10.090
[NOTE PLAYING]

00:34:10.090 --> 00:34:11.020
ALAN STEWART: The second.

00:34:11.020 --> 00:34:11.410
[NOTE PLAYING]

