Sorry.

00:34:44.850 --> 00:34:45.380
It goes--

00:34:45.380 --> 00:34:54.054
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:34:54.054 --> 00:34:57.380
ALAN STEWART: And that rhythm
I thought sounded good.

00:34:57.380 --> 00:34:59.765
And that's what I
