Or was that part of pi as well,
that little thing you do

00:35:03.577 --> 00:35:03.705
with your left hand?

00:35:03.705 --> 00:35:06.170
Or is that just a little bit of
a flourish you put in for

00:35:06.170 --> 00:35:06.980
musical reasons?

00:35:06.980 --> 00:35:11.460
ALAN STEWART: That was the arty,
