00:35:32.430 --> 00:35:33.380
ALAN STEWART: Yeah.

00:35:33.380 --> 00:35:34.860
Yeah.

00:35:34.860 --> 00:35:37.490
The tempo, the number of
beats per minute, was

00:35:37.490 --> 00:35:40.200
some multiple of pi.

